snippet.title: Racing Into The Night x Cinderella | Mashup of YOASOBI, CIDER GIRL (Komi Can't Communicate)
snippet.description:
"Racing Into The Night x Cinderella" contains the following:
1. YOASOBI - Racing Into The Night "Yoru ni Kakeru" (Utagoe Acapella)
2. CIDER GIRL - Cinderella "Komi Can't Communicate - Opening Theme" (Official Instrumental)
